name: Dental Services - Check website or call for Lottery Dates
short_desc: Provides free dental examination, cleaning, filling, and simple extraction
description: New patients, refer to the new client intake system, known as dental lottery. Call or check website under "Dental" for lottery dates. Lottery winners will receive an initial exam the same night. Services provided: dental examination and check-ups, dental cleanings, x-ray services, fillings, plastic/composite, metal/amalgam and simple extractions.
